graph TD
    subgraph Data Loading
    A[Raw PDF / HTML / TXT] --> B[LangChain Document Loader]
    B -->|Returns raw string + metadata| C[Raw Document Object]
    end
    
    subgraph Chunking Phase
    C --> D[RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter]
    D -->|Chunk Size: 1000| E[Chunks 1..N]
    D -->|Overlap: 200| E
    end
    
    subgraph Indexing Phase
    E --> F[Embedding Model]
    F --> G[(VectorStore: FAISS/Pinecone)]
    end
    
    subgraph Retriever Interface
    H[User Query] --> I[vectorstore.as_retriever]
    I -->|Embeds Query| G
    G -->|Returns Top Chunks| I
    I --> J[Formatted Context string]
    end
